             was indicted for <rs id="t18271025-47-off300" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18271025-47-off300" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18271025-47-off300" type="offenceSubcategory" value="manslaughter"></interp>
